<p>It's been a while since Ive done raw webrtc. I am trying to get the local video from my webcam. I quickly made this <a href="https://jsfiddle.net/bmLdmfkh/" rel="nofollow">https://jsfiddle.net/bmLdmfkh/</a></p>  <pre><code>$( document ).ready(function() {     var video = document.getElementById('video');     navigator.webkitGetUserMedia(         { video: true },         function(stream) {             console.log('stream', stream);             video.src = URL.createObjectURL(stream);             video.play();         },         function(err) {             console.log("An error occured! " + err);         }     ); }); </code></pre>  <p>seems to work on js fiddle but when running on localhost with a python server, it does not ask if I want to start sharing my webcam </p>